com.differ.differcore.service

Class SaveServiceImpl

  • com.differ.differcore.service.SaveServiceImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SaveService

    @Service
public class SaveServiceImpl
implements SaveService

    Implementation of interface SaveService interface.

    Service uses springfox.documentation.spring.web.DocumentationCache from springfox to get full description of API. It saves this description in file system.

    See Also:
